longBusinessSummary: Oriental Food Industries Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures, markets, and sells snack food and confectionery products in Malaysia, rest of Asia, and internationally. The company offers wafers, cakes, biscuits, potato snacks, and bakery products under the Rota, Super Ring, Jacker, Oriental, Fudo, Delio, ZESS, and Funtos brand names. It is also involved in the property development activities. The company was founded in 1978 and is headquartered in Malacca, Malaysia.
